snippet.title: Zeph - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Zeph is a puzzle exploration game developed by student game dev team Grannus Games.

Use Zeph's powers of the sun to traverse the environment, bend reality and gravity to your will all in order to bring the Sun Mosaic pieces back together and breathe life back into the sun and the planet Brudeon which is sustains.

Add to your Steam Wishlist!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1279810/Zeph/

Follow the development of Zeph across our social medias @GrannusGames
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GrannusGAMES
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/grannusgames/?hl=en
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GrannusGames/

Business contact:
grannusgames@gmail.com

Visit our website at:
https://grannusgames.com/
